satellite.heading: Satelite
satellite.specs:
Fua: 50x58x64 mm
1P PocketQube
mamafa: 245 gr
Mea: alumini, auro, fiberglass, ma mea faaeletonika.
Ta'amilosaga: Maualuluga 525 ± 25 km; fa'alogona: SSO 97.6 ± 0.1°
Launcher: PSLV (Polar Satellite Launch Vehicle) fa'atautaia e ISRO

antenna.heading: Antenna/Vatagata
antenna.specs:
Lua: 6m (diamita) e 1.2m (maualuga)
Mamafa: 46 kg
Mea: alumini, laupapa fa'ata epoxy, fa'aumu alumini auro o lo'o fa'apipi'iina i se fausaga fa'a.
